   Starting a Business
     __________________________________________________________________



   Man holding a telephone.

   The links on this page provide information about what is involved in
   starting a business and bring up some important issues to consider. Be
   sure to review the "Checklist for Starting a Business," which lists
   typical pre-start actions.

